            <li class="jobs-listing">to process your registration with the Services, including verifying your information is active and valid;</li>
            <li class="jobs-listing">to improve the Services or our services, to customize your experience with the Services, or to serve you specific content that is most relevant to you;</li>
            <li class="jobs-listing">to enable you to participate in a variety of the Services’ features such as online or mobile promotions;</li>
